com.tailf.dp

Interface DpNanoServiceCallback

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NanoServiceCallbackProxy

    public interface DpNanoServiceCallback
    This interface is used for the Nano Service callbacks. These callbacks are registered in conjuntion with the defined plan_components and plan_component_states of a Nano service plan
    See Also:
    Dp.registerAnnotatedCallbacks(Object)
